column2: 1. Do you have a social media account? (e.g., Facebook, Twitter, etc.)
column3: 2. Which social media account do you use usually?
column4: 3. Which device do you usually use to connect social media?
column5: 4. Which type of internet connection do you use?
column6: 5. How long have you been using a social media account?
column7: 6. How frequently do you post (upload status or add photos/videos) on social media?
column8: 7. How much time do you spend daily in social media?
column9: 8. When do you usually use social media?
column10: 9. How many friends do you have on social media?
column11: 10. How many friends do you know personally in social media?
column12: 11. How many groups you are tagged in social media?
column13: 12. What is your main purpose for using social media (e.g. Facebook)?
column14: 13. What contents do you mainly look for in your social media news feed?
column15: 14.Do you believe social media is a good thing?
column16: 15. When you see something in social media, do you instantly believe it?
column17: 16. Have you ever experienced peer pressure due to social media?
column18: 17. Does your emotion get influenced by other's posts (success, failure, loss)?
column19: 18. Have you ever compared yourself with other’s success or luxurious life?
column20: 19. Do you think, your mental wellbeing would be better if you do not use social media?
column21: 20. If answer is yes, are you trying to control that thing and trying to reduce the use of social media?
column22: 21. Please write your age in years (number).
